description:
Danny recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules with the help of makeup artist extraordinaire Jared Lipscomb! They discuss Stassi's engagement, Scheana's willingness to film a scene hitting on Stassi's little brother, a softball game that lasted for what felt like a lifetime, and lots more!
